claim.claim-text:
1. An electronic input device comprising:
a tip for contacting a physical document;
a sensor to record movement of the tip relative to the physical document;
a recognition component to recognize one or more characters formed during recorded movement of the tip, the one or more characters corresponding to an electronically-executable instruction; and
a processor to automatically cause execution of the electronically-executable instruction upon recognizing the electronically-executable instruction from the one or more characters formed during the recorded movement of the tip.
